**Weather**: A north wind howls, dark clouds blot out the moon, with occasional scattered raindrops falling', 'draft', NULL, 'provider_c86aa37930fd4a56a1d0cf549a62e2a0', 0, '3ae6f93ece354ab48e03b3c19f132256', 'default', 'default', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'v1', '2026-03-01 09:44:15.611576+00', '2026-03-01 09:28:47.042288+00', '2026-03-01 09:44:15.646566+00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
