**Location**: The entrance of Wang Family Village, under the old locust tree  
**Weather**: A north wind howls, dark clouds obscure the moon, occasional scattered raindrops fall', 'draft', NULL, 'provider_c86aa37930fd4a56a1d0cf549a62e2a0', 0, '207f4eaaf06447d2ba510373dca2954d', 'default', 'default', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'v1', '2026-03-01 09:28:45.332919+00', '2026-03-01 09:23:19.243047+00', '2026-03-01 09:28:45.356331+00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
